WEBVTT

00:09.970 --> 00:11.792
A hein? Haa.

00:11.875 --> 00:14.958
Woah-ho-ho!

00:18.625 --> 00:19.570
Sanites, sé?

00:20.720 --> 00:21.696
Pouah! Pf.

00:22.004 --> 00:22.867
Naa. Mat sita.

00:23.271 --> 00:25.410
Casupa ti. Ova sa ta-ta.

00:25.680 --> 00:27.195
Un baba si, hein?

00:27.284 --> 00:31.048
Esekita! Eh patika. A zizi!

00:31.125 --> 00:35.333
Eh, veux-tu, oui. Eh sawa ti. A tita pata!

00:36.417 --> 00:37.667
Coma sacin.
- Hein?

00:39.229 --> 00:40.580
Store Parak.

00:45.334 --> 00:48.000
Pouah! C'est Karik. Sakating.

00:48.000 --> 00:49.375
Et tone ecco.

00:49.458 --> 00:51.083
Eh laka ti na ti qa.

00:51.167 --> 00:52.333
Eh rocka tocka tique.

00:52.417 --> 00:53.833
Eh yo qure kara!

00:53.917 --> 00:55.625
Nyage siqo tacke.

00:57.818 --> 01:02.125
- Jo pa sa tava!
Ah, siga stagger.

01:02.208 --> 01:03.458
Sépa aussi!

01:03.938 --> 01:05.750
Glorckling startrick!

01:05.830 --> 01:08.083
- Eh para kiri gouratick
- Se passa.

01:08.170 --> 01:11.000
- Katchu un ti-tat.
- Pfft, pouah.

01:11.083 --> 01:14.792
Hé, c'est un “pouah”. B-- Batgar a barsoba, n'est-ce pas?

01:14.880 --> 01:19.625
- "Ah see tur, eh patuse."
- "Touré-heure."

01:19.709 --> 01:22.042
- “Ana ma kin a poura doura.”

01:22.125 --> 01:23.708
- Marke bou!

01:23.792 --> 01:24.736
A tu tit.

01:25.225 --> 01:26.917
- Regardez-ça Danik.

01:27.000 --> 01:28.333
Ugh!
Ugh!

01:29.680 --> 01:31.210
Ohh! Mmm.

01:31.290 --> 01:33.375
Bo ro lat d'un Coac.

01:33.470 --> 01:35.625
- Woah, la ba li bi de Coac.

01:35.708 --> 01:41.542
Ugh! Coac est un froidig.
Eh sata ta-ta?

01:41.625 --> 01:42.667
Eh Sinqa Tong.

01:42.750 --> 01:43.958
Zatick!
Blugh.

01:44.042 --> 01:44.917
Ta-ti!
- Zagh!

01:45.000 --> 01:47.375
Mourkats!
A ta-tara.

01:47.458 --> 01:48.583
Ugh…

01:48.670 --> 01:50.167
- Krinka!
Asita.

01:50.250 --> 01:51.583
Pour le Roi.
- Maman Dante.

01:51.667 --> 01:53.167
Zaldor!
Mal Pato.

01:53.250 --> 01:55.042
Philippe Cots.
- Ma Toupit.

01:56.240 --> 02:00.766
Masiq et non et bleu.
Ta-ba ta-ba tou-be di?

02:01.292 --> 02:03.500
Arata, azit!

02:05.595 --> 02:06.958
Eh, oh! Oh!

02:07.042 --> 02:07.486
Oye.

02:09.128 --> 02:10.000
Waha aha.

02:10.080 --> 02:12.125
Non, bla, non.
Et ça?

02:12.210 --> 02:13.833
- Woah!
Ouais!

02:13.917 --> 02:16.375
Za Bornak.
Un Pasa aussi, un rire.

02:16.783 --> 02:18.917
Euh…
- Eh, beaucoup de Shorplee!

02:19.000 --> 02:21.125
Waouh.

02:21.208 --> 02:23.667
- Yo, ho, ho, ho. Ooh. Coac!

02:23.750 --> 02:24.833
Coac?!

02:24.917 --> 02:26.833
Zaba gothique.
A suba ti-ta.

02:26.917 --> 02:30.083
Cochez le sac. Allez ba tincka combat.

02:35.110 --> 02:37.566
- “Banezinkat”?
Bada bouta vouda.

02:37.670 --> 02:38.875
Too too.

03:07.417 --> 03:10.040
- Coac.
